a">Lisa</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/blackpink-lisa-cryptic-coming-soon-teaser-instagram-3583632">在她的 Instagram 帐户上发布了一条神秘的预告片</a>，就在一个月前，YG Entertainment 证实她和她的乐队成员<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/blackpink-not-renewing-individual-contracts-yg-entertainment-3563895">不会与该机构续签个人合同</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/red-velvet-irene-renew-contract-sm-entertainment-3583638">Red Velvet 的 Irene 与 SM Entertainment 续约的</a>消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
